parameters:
\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>This year's end-of-year party reception... I won't be able
to go with Saki anymore.
\nc<Senpai>Yes, I wonder if this was the right decision...

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>...It's nothing. I'm counting on you to look after the
office until we return.
\nc<Saki>Yes! Please... take care on your way.

\nc<Saki>(It's good that I'm not involved in the event anymore... but
somehow the atmosphere feels heavy this time.)

\nc<Saki>(It must be a very important event, right? I hope it ends
safely.)
